(254, 'Chronic Inflammatory Autoimmune Conditions', 'Psoriasis', '7128', 'TNFAIP3', 'GG', 'The TNFAIP3 gene encodes A20, a TNF-alpha-inducible zinc finger protein. A20 plays an important role in the negative feedback regulation of NF-kappa B (nuclear factor kappa light-chain enhancer of activated B cells) signalling, as a negative immunoregulat', 'https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed?LinkName=gene_pubmed&from_uid=7128', 'rs610604', 5),
